              "description": {
                "text": "1. Implement rate limiting on form submissions (e.g., max 5 submissions per IP per minute). 2. Add CAPTCHA to prevent automated submissions. 3. Implement a minimum time between submissions per session. 4. This is secondary to fixing the stored XSS vulnerability itself."
