              "description": {
                "text": "Implement account lockout after 5 failed attempts (temporary lockout of 15-30 minutes). Add progressive delays between attempts. Consider implementing CAPTCHA after 3 failed attempts. Log and alert on repeated failed login attempts from same IP. Implement IP-based rate limiting."
              }
            }
          ]
