              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "**CloudTrail logs** include a **metric filter** for trail configuration events (`CreateTrail`, `UpdateTrail`, `DeleteTrail`, `StartLogging`, `StopLogging`) with an associated **CloudWatch alarm** to alert on matches.\n\nEvaluates the presence of this filter-and-alarm monitoring."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://hub.prowler.com/check/cloudwatch_log_metric_filter_and_alarm_for_cloudtrail_configuration_changes_enabled",
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CLOUDWATCH_LOG_METRIC_FILTER_AUTHENTICATION_FAILURES",
              "name": "cloudwatch_log_metric_filter_authentication_failures",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Account has a CloudWatch Logs metric filter and alarm for AWS Management Console authentication failures"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "CloudWatch Logs metric filter and alarm for **AWS Management Console authentication failures**, sourced from CloudTrail (`eventName=ConsoleLogin`, `errorMessage=\"Failed authentication\"`).\n\nIdentifies whether these failures are converted into a metric and actively monitored by an alarm."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://hub.prowler.com/check/cloudwatch_log_metric_filter_authentication_failures",
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CLOUDWATCH_LOG_METRIC_FILTER_AWS_ORGANIZATIONS_CHANGES",
              "name": "cloudwatch_log_metric_filter_aws_organizations_changes",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CloudWatch Logs metric filter and alarm exist for AWS Organizations changes"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "**CloudWatch Logs** metric filters and alarms monitor **AWS Organizations** change events recorded by CloudTrail, including actions like `CreateAccount`, `AttachPolicy`, `MoveAccount`, and `UpdateOrganizationalUnit`.\n\nThe evaluation looks for a filter on the trail log group matching `organizations.amazonaws.com` events and an alarm linked to that metric."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://hub.prowler.com/check/cloudwatch_log_metric_filter_aws_organizations_changes",
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              }
